You could just pull up to the

37:29.681 --> 37:31.816
beach any time you wanted and

37:31.817 --> 37:36.621
look out and see the
end of complications.

37:36.622 --> 37:40.725
And anybody could do that
and it was safe and free.

37:40.726 --> 37:48.333
And I thought, that's a
this is beautiful.

